data.name: label6.Text
data.value:
Ingesting assets in Bulk involves decoupling asset creation from the upload process.
1) Specify a name for the bulk ingest container 2) Declare the asset and files to upload by selecting the files or folders 3) Edit the asset names and reorganize the files in assets as needed 4) Optional: files can be encrypted locally before the upload. In that case, they are copied to a new folder 5) Use the upload method of your choice to upload the associated files to the bulk ingest container 6) Azure Media Services will automatically complete the asset creation
